Package: BaRcodes
Title: Custom R tools for collection, tracking, and curation of biological samples using 1D or 2D barcodes
Version: 0.0.0.9100
Authors@R: c(person("Robert", "Colautti", email = "robert.colautti@queensu.ca", role = c("aut", "cre")), 
    person("Emily", "Bao", role="aut"), person("Yihan", "Wu", role="aut"))
Description: Tools to create labels for biological samples. The creation of 
    labels and pdf files for printing on sticker sheets is guided by user 
    prompts. Both one-level and hierarchical labels can be created. 
Depends: 
    R (>= 3.4.2)
License: GPL-2
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports:
    ggplot2,
    grDevices,
    grid,
    qrcode
Suggests: testthat,
    knitr,
    rmarkdown
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
VignetteBuilder: knitr
